, Ryan R. Holston argues for the need to cultivate these historically-rooted and local relationships and the shared meanings to which they give life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 07. Mrz 2024) 0aDeliberative democracyxPhilosophy. 4aCommunication : Communication. 4aPolitics and Law : Democracy. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Philosophy. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Theory. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / History & Theory.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package 2023z978311149193640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143849210040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438492100423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438492100/original  a978-3-11-149193-6  SUNY Press eBook Package 2023b2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles